00:17:14.069 --> 00:17:14.079
Alborz

00:17:14.079 --> 00:17:16.390
mountains surrounding Tehran. The target

00:17:16.400 --> 00:17:18.789
was chosen for a specific reason. Buried

00:17:18.799 --> 00:17:20.549
deep beneath the mountains, Iran has

00:17:20.559 --> 00:17:22.549
